Team Name: Swarm Router
Team Description: A swarm router that routes tasks to the appropriate agents
These are the agents in your team. Each agent has a specific role and expertise to contribute to the team's objectives.
Total Agents: 6

Below is a summary of your team members and their primary responsibilities:
| Agent Name | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| Research Manager | Manages research operations and coordinates research tasks |
| Data Analyst | Analyzes data and generates insights |
| Research Assistant | Assists with research tasks and data collection |
| Development Manager | Manages development projects and coordinates development tasks |
| Software Engineer | Develops and implements software solutions |
| QA Engineer | Tests and ensures quality of software |

Each agent is designed to handle tasks within their area of expertise. Collaborate effectively by assigning tasks according to these roles.
Write a research paper on the impact of AI on the future of work
